{"tid":2334641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"少年中秋違宵禁還柙候審 辯方以賀冬至慶生日為由 再度申請保釋獲批准","createTime":"2020-12-21T09:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T10:24:01.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d50d35dccb8a67ee57686fb3fd4fe7e4d33dae13","tid":2334641,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日有網民發起「三罷」，多區發生衝突，其間兩名年青年涉在旺角管有雷射筆及伸縮棍，被控管有適合作非法用途工具罪 。案件今在西九龍裁判法院審前覆核，辯方為其中一名早前因在中秋翌日違反宵禁保釋條件、因而被取消擔保的青年再次申請保釋，指被告已經知錯及反省，加上今晚是冬至，明天更是被告生日，希望法庭給予機會，讓被告保釋候審。主任裁判官羅德泉考慮後批准保釋。"},{"pid":"7d7120f1d7e7fb689e8286b2dc6b92c026d49ce7","tid":2334641,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/AJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FAJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=0ae21d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FAJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ%2F&h=5803cdd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/AJTPAABLRRGOVOS6CYIBQ5BTWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"9a4ab2e011759093a293edb7d860fcf6c2943da4","tid":2334641,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b8cfebfdc0ed68ad35f0f4d0bf9d80d83d0db1","tid":2334641,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"辯方大狀代表被告多次向法庭致歉，並指今晚是冬至，而明天是被告生日，加上審訊排到明年4月，如果繼續將被告還柙，<span class=\"red\">他接受審訊時將會已經還柙超過6個月。</span>"},{"pid":"c23afb8607757e7f13b04f8709031bf924b63e63","tid":2334641,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT